ou chamo a Sandra Felgueiras !

240
00:16:25.880 --> 00:16:27.440
Que mal tem ?

241
00:16:28.120 --> 00:16:29.720
Que mal tem ?!

242
00:16:30.920 --> 00:16:33.720
